quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  33,60,"Asi vanyengedzi, neavo mumoyo yavo mune chirwere (cheupombwe), uye avo vanofambisa makuhwa kubva pavanhu vemuMadeenah vakasasiya, zvirokwazvo, tichakuita kuti uvakurire, uye zvirokwazvo havazombokwanisa kugaramo savavakidzani vako asi kusara kwekanguva kadiki"
  33,61,"Vachatsvinyirwa, uye vachange vari vanorwadziswa kwese kwavanenge vari, uye vachauraiwa zvakanyanya"
  33,62,"Ndiyo yaiva nzira yaAllah panguva yeavo vakapfuura, uye hauzombowana kana imwe shanduko panzira yaAllah"
  33,63,"Vanhu vakakuvhunza maererano nenguva, taura kuti: “Ruzivo rwayo runongova naAllah chete. Unombozivei! Inokwanisa (nguva) kunge iri pedyo!”"
  33,64,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vakasvora (vakarengera) vanhu vasingatendi, uye vakavagadzirira moto unopisa"
  33,65,"Umo mavachagara zvachose, uye havafi vakawana muchengetedzi kana mubatsiri"
  33,66,"Pazuva iro zviso zvavo zvichatendeudzwa mumoto, vachataura kuti: “Imi ingadai takateerera Allah uye nemutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)).”"
  33,67,"Uye vachataura kuti: “Tenzi vedu! Zvirokwazvo, takave tinoteerera vatungamiriri nevakuru vedu, naizvozvo vakatiburitsa munzira (yakatwasuka).”"
  33,68,“Tenzi vedu! Vapei marwadzo kaviri uye movarengera kurengera kukuru!”
  33,69,"Imi vatendi! Musaite seavo vakasvota Musa. Asi Allah vakamuchenesa pamusoro peizvo zvavaitaura, uye akava munhu akakosha pamberi paAllah"
  33,70,"Imi vatendi! Itai basa renyu kuna Allah uye kuvatya, uye taurai chokwadi (nguva dzose)"
  33,71,"Vachaita kuti mabasa enyu ave akanaka uye vokuregererai zvitadzo zvenyu. Uye uyo ari upi zvake anoteerera Allah nemutumwa wavo (SAW), zvirokwazvo, anenge abudirira kubudirira kukuru (achanunurwa kubva kumoto uye opinzwa muParadhiso)"
  33,72,"Zvirokwazvo, takave tinopa Al-Amaanah (Basa) kumatenga nenyika uye nemakomo, asi zvakaramba kuritakura uye zvikaritya (zvichitya murango waAllah), asi vanhu vakaritakura. Zvirokwazvo, vakazvidzvanyirira uye vari bundu"
  33,73,"Kuitira kuti Allah vazorwadzisa vanyengedzi vechirume nevechikadzi uye maMushrikoon (vasingatendi muumwechete waAllah). Uye Allah vacharegerera vanotenda (muIslaam) varume nemadzimai. Uye Allah vane ruregerero rukuru, nenyasha zhinji"
  34,1,"Kurumbidzwa nekutendwa ndekwaAllah, avo ndivo muridzi wezvese zviri mumatenga nenyika. Kurumbidzwa nekutendwa ndekwavo muhupenyu hunotevera. Uye ndivo muchenjeri, uye muzivi wezvose"
  34,2,"Vanoziva zvinopinda pasi uye zvinobuda mariri, uye zvinodzika kubva kudenga nezvinokwira kwariri. Uye ndivo vane tsitsi dzose, neruregerero"
  34,3,"Avo vasingatendi vanoti: “Nguva (yekutongwa) haiuye kwatiri.” Taura: “Hongu! Ndinopika naTenzi vangu, muzivi wezvisingaoneki, ichauya kwamuri. Hapana kanhu kadiki pauremu kana kurema kushoma kune ikako kana kukura kukadarika chingatiza ruzivo rwavo mumatenga kana pasi, asi kuti chiri mugwaro rakajeka (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh).”"
  34,4,Kuti vave vanopa mubairo kune avo vanotenda (muhumwechete waAllah) nekuita mabasa akanaka. Vakadaro vachawana ruregerero uye neraramo yakanaka (Paradhiso)
  34,5,"Asi avo vanotsungirira mukupikisa ndima dzedu nekudzishingaidza, ivo vachave vanowana mutongo unorwadza"
  34,6,"Uye avo vakapuhwa ruzivo vanoona zvakadzikiswa kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) kubva kuna Tenzi vako kuti ichokwadi, uye zvinotungamira kunzira yeMukuru, neMurumbidzwi"
  34,7,"Avo vasingatendi vanoti: “Tingakutungamirirei kune murume (Muhammad (SAW)) uyo anokuudzai (kuti) kana maitwa ivhu mave zvimedu zvimedu, chokwadi muchasikwa (zvekare) patsva?”"
  34,8,"Asi aunza manyepo pamusoro paAllah kana kuti mune kupenga maari? Kwete! Asi vasingatendi muhupenyu hwemangwana ndivo (pachavo) vari mumarwadzo, uye vakarasika zvakanyanya"
  34,9,"Havaoni zviri mberi nemumashure mavo, zvedenga nepasi? Kana tikada, tinonyudza pasi navo, kana kuita kuti zvimedu zvedenga zvivadonhere. Zvirokwazvo, mune izvozvo mune chiratidzo kune wese muranda anotendeukira kuna Allah (achikumbira rugerero)"